# Tech Stack and Versions

- Framework: Next.js 15.3.4 (App Router)
- Runtime: React 19, React DOM 19
- Language: TypeScript 5.8.3 (strict, noEmit)
- Styling: Tailwind CSS 4 via `@tailwindcss/postcss`, `tw-animate-css`
- UI Primitives: Radix UI (`@radix-ui/react-*`)
- UI Patterns: shadcn-inspired (`components/ui/*`, `class-variance-authority`, `tailwind-merge`, `clsx`)
- Icons: `lucide-react`, `@icons-pack/react-simple-icons`
- Linting: ESLint 9, `eslint-config-next` 15.3.4 (flat config)
- Dev Server: `next dev --turbopack`
- Fonts: `next/font` (Inter)

Key configs
- `next.config.ts`: minimal export
- `postcss.config.mjs`: `plugins: ["@tailwindcss/postcss"]`
- `tsconfig.json`: bundler moduleResolution, path alias `@/*`

Lockfiles present
- `bun.lock` and `package-lock.json` exist; scripts use `next`, so `bun run dev` or `npm run dev` both work.
